.git
.github
.gitlab-ci.yml
.circleci
.gitpod.yml

# Claude / agent meta
.agents
.claude
**/CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.OPTIONAL.md
**/AGENTS.md
**/AGENTS.CLOUD.md

# Editor
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo
