**/node_modules
**/.parcel-cache
**/dist
webapp/channels/dist
webapp/platform/*/dist
server/bin
server/dist

# Test / e2e ne treba runtime image-u
e2e-tests
api
tools
**/*.test.go
**/*_test.go
**/__tests__
**/cypress
**/playwright

# Logs / data
*.log
logs/
data/

# Docs
**/*.md
!server/scripts/config_generator/**

